WEBVTT

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:11.300
(October 13, 2025)

00:00:13.890 --> 00:00:14.890
Wow.

00:00:15.520 --> 00:00:16.840
These are great.

00:00:17.569 --> 00:00:19.329
Yeah, everyone looks so happy.

00:00:20.709 --> 00:00:23.019
Wataru really has a gift for this.

00:00:24.309 --> 00:00:25.780
So reliable.

00:00:36.250 --> 00:00:37.350
It's already...

00:00:37.650 --> 00:00:38.750
been two weeks...

00:00:38.959 --> 00:00:40.289
since I last reached out.

00:00:41.419 --> 00:00:42.619
I can't see you right now.

00:00:44.860 --> 00:00:45.860
Because if I do,

00:00:47.139 --> 00:00:49.219
I won't be able to hide
how much I love you.

00:00:59.189 --> 00:01:00.440
Welcome.

00:01:00.819 --> 00:01:03.400
I'm afraid I have some bad news.

00:01:03.869 --> 00:01:05.069
That sounds ominous.

00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:07.399
That apartment I showed you...

00:01:08.209 --> 00:01:10.529
it's already been rented out.

00:01:11.330 --> 00:01:14.089
But I have a few other
places I can show you.

00:01:14.680 --> 00:01:15.680
Oh...

00:01:16.220 --> 00:01:19.079
- Sorry, I haven't talked to Minato yet.
- I see.

00:01:20.540 --> 00:01:22.180
Didn't Minato's grandpa get hospitalized?

00:01:22.410 --> 00:01:25.733
- I heard he's out already, but he's probably busy.
- Wait, what?

00:01:26.620 --> 00:01:27.989
You didn't know?

00:01:28.522 --> 00:01:30.442
I ran into Minato at the
hospital the other day.

00:01:31.150 --> 00:01:32.710
He said he was there visiting.

00:01:34.489 --> 00:01:35.589
Oh, I see.

00:01:37.129 --> 00:01:38.229
He probably just...

00:01:38.610 --> 00:01:41.180
didn't want to worry you or something.

00:01:41.550 --> 00:01:42.550
Wow.

00:01:42.769 --> 00:01:43.969
I think I've said too much.

00:01:44.199 --> 00:01:45.155
No, it's fine...

00:01:45.192 --> 00:01:47.850
Hey! Listen to this!

00:01:47.930 --> 00:01:49.255
The reason *I* was at the hospital...

00:01:49.279 --> 00:01:50.379
Come on, ask me why.

00:01:51.790 --> 00:01:52.686
Were you sick?

00:01:52.711 --> 00:01:56.010
No, I was just there with someone.

00:01:57.599 --> 00:01:58.599
Actually,

00:02:00.160 --> 00:02:01.500
my wife is pregnant!

00:02:02.330 --> 00:02:03.730
Oh! Congratulations!

00:02:04.236 --> 00:02:05.796
It's really surprising.

00:02:06.069 --> 00:02:08.800
Life really does change
in the blink of an eye.

00:02:09.820 --> 00:02:11.870
But man, once the baby comes...

00:02:12.649 --> 00:02:13.649
strollers and all that...

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:17.160
Why?

00:02:18.600 --> 00:02:19.600
Oh!

00:02:19.601 --> 00:02:21.010
Let me go grab the album samples.

00:02:21.910 --> 00:02:22.910
Right.

00:02:23.199 --> 00:02:24.560
That's what I came here for.

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:13.000
"Countdown To Yes"

00:03:14.300 --> 00:03:16.100
(Episode 9)

00:03:16.199 --> 00:03:17.199
Oh, thanks.

00:03:18.210 --> 00:03:19.960
That's much better.

00:03:20.639 --> 00:03:22.484
- How are you feeling?
- Not too bad.

00:03:24.470 --> 00:03:25.660
All right, all right.

00:03:26.139 --> 00:03:28.589
It's snack time!

00:03:29.210 --> 00:03:30.210
Mmm.

00:03:30.500 --> 00:03:32.520
Here you go.

00:03:32.750 --> 00:03:34.720
- Orange jelly. This brings back memories.
- Yeah.

00:03:35.330 --> 00:03:37.820
- You used to love this, didn't you, Minato?
- I did.

00:03:38.289 --> 00:03:41.269
Grandpa's is the low-sugar version.

00:03:44.360 --> 00:03:45.600
- Let's eat.
- Okay.

00:03:48.619 --> 00:03:49.619
Mmm.

00:03:50.949 --> 00:03:51.949
It's good.

00:03:53.639 --> 00:03:54.639
Well then,

00:03:54.669 --> 00:03:57.922
I'll dig in too.

00:04:01.809 --> 00:04:03.559
Mmm.

00:04:04.580 --> 00:04:05.480
You should've waited...

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:08.389
until I was dressed up to take a photo.

00:04:08.414 --> 00:04:10.530
That would've been boring.

00:04:10.550 --> 00:04:11.757
Honestly.

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:14.373
Oh, look.

00:04:14.460 --> 00:04:16.279
Even Minato is laughing at me.

00:04:17.410 --> 00:04:19.730
It's just because you said the
exact same thing back then.

00:04:20.329 --> 00:04:22.870
I think we were eating
orange jelly that day, too.

00:04:25.559 --> 00:04:27.539
Back when I was in elementary school.

00:04:28.500 --> 00:04:29.379
Oh.

00:04:29.380 --> 00:04:31.659
That was the day Grandpa
first let me borrow his camera.

00:04:32.089 --> 00:04:33.339
You actually remember that?

00:04:34.579 --> 00:04:36.070
I might have a photo of it.

00:04:37.459 --> 00:04:38.549
Let me see...

00:04:39.260 --> 00:04:40.260
Hmm... Oh.

00:04:40.489 --> 00:04:41.589
It should be around here.

00:04:42.820 --> 00:04:43.820
Yeah.

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:48.000
Mmm-hmm.

00:04:49.119 --> 00:04:50.820
It's gotta be right around...

00:04:52.400 --> 00:04:54.044
(Tea set placed with
millimeter precision) (Struggling

00:04:54.068 --> 00:04:56.085
with the latest kettle) (Miyako
carefully cooling her tea)

00:04:56.109 --> 00:04:57.109
This is it, right?

00:04:58.279 --> 00:04:59.279
Yeah.

00:04:59.470 --> 00:05:00.470
This was the day.

00:05:11.279 --> 00:05:12.379
I'm home!

00:05:12.429 --> 00:05:13.529
Welcome back.

00:05:18.250 --> 00:05:19.250
What's this?

00:05:19.459 --> 00:05:20.459
A photo album.

00:05:20.700 --> 00:05:21.959
It's all Grandma.

00:05:23.350 --> 00:05:24.450
Because every single day,

00:05:24.459 --> 00:05:26.309
I take a picture of her.

00:05:26.670 --> 00:05:31.240
I told you to wait until I look nice!

00:05:31.670 --> 00:05:33.492
- Minato, want some?
- Yeah!

00:05:33.493 --> 00:05:35.729
But that's not the point.

00:05:36.029 --> 00:05:37.029
Ha!

00:05:37.170 --> 00:05:38.770
So that's how it was.

00:05:39.589 --> 00:05:43.119
You could let me look
elegant once in a while.

00:05:43.190 --> 00:05:44.590
Right, Minato?

00:05:45.320 --> 00:05:48.269
Oh, stop it already!

00:05:48.459 --> 00:05:50.159
I'll go get some tea.

00:05:50.230 --> 00:05:51.330
You two go ahead and eat.

00:05:59.390 --> 00:06:00.470
They're great, aren't they?

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:01.869
The photos Grandpa takes.

00:06:02.829 --> 00:06:04.295
She might not be all dressed up,

00:06:04.296 --> 00:06:05.791
but she looks lovely in every single one.

00:06:05.815 --> 00:06:06.815
You can tell, huh?

00:06:07.600 --> 00:06:10.360
I'm always thinking "how
cute" when I snap the shutter.

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:13.966
But don't tell Grandma I said that.

00:06:13.990 --> 00:06:15.760
- It's a secret.
- Okay.

00:06:17.089 --> 00:06:19.070
What are you two whispering about?

00:06:20.040 --> 00:06:21.059
It's a secret!

00:06:21.670 --> 00:06:23.860
Oh, for heaven's sake.

00:06:25.100 --> 00:06:26.570
Here's your tea.

00:06:27.859 --> 00:06:28.950
Oh, Minato.

00:06:29.339 --> 00:06:31.760
- Give Grandma a bite too.
- Okay.

00:06:36.119 --> 00:06:37.190
This is delicious.

00:06:43.450 --> 00:06:44.896
Minato, do you want to try taking a photo?

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:45.720
Yeah!

00:06:45.779 --> 00:06:46.779
Okay.

00:06:47.429 --> 00:06:48.429
There.

00:06:50.730 --> 00:06:51.969
Hey, that was my piece!

00:06:53.993 --> 00:06:55.260
Here you go.

00:06:55.369 --> 00:06:56.369
Thanks.

00:06:56.700 --> 00:06:59.900
(The first photo Minato ever took)

00:07:00.100 --> 00:07:01.600
(Miyako Today: 2010-2018)

00:07:02.209 --> 00:07:03.409
- Is it good?
- Yeah.

00:07:04.109 --> 00:07:06.069
It's good, but it's definitely
not sweet enough.

00:07:06.640 --> 00:07:09.228
- It's plenty sweet.
- No way.

00:07:09.229 --> 00:07:11.349
Lately, everything you eat
is basically a sugar cube.

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:13.670
Grandpa has always...

00:07:13.950 --> 00:07:16.309
watched Grandma from
the closest possible distance.

00:07:19.279 --> 00:07:20.820
Capturing every single day...

00:07:20.989 --> 00:07:23.679
of her life.

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:25.600
That's so nice.

00:07:31.790 --> 00:07:32.990
I want to do that too.

00:07:33.540 --> 00:07:35.390
I want to capture Wataru's everyday life.

00:07:42.290 --> 00:07:43.290
Oh...

00:07:45.799 --> 00:07:47.360
Are you tired?

00:07:48.220 --> 00:07:50.755
- Why don't you go rest for a bit?
- Okay.

00:07:51.679 --> 00:07:53.495
- Can you take care of this?
- Sure.

00:07:58.359 --> 00:07:59.900
Oh, thank you.

00:08:01.089 --> 00:08:02.089
Let's go.

00:08:03.309 --> 00:08:06.240
I know you're happy Minato came to visit,

00:08:06.459 --> 00:08:08.969
- but you can't overdo it yet.
- I know.

00:08:09.264 --> 00:08:10.877
I want to be there, in the front row...

00:08:12.119 --> 00:08:13.999
watching Wataru's life unfold.

00:08:32.239 --> 00:08:34.869
- Do you want to help?
- No...

00:08:35.308 --> 00:08:36.789
I have no idea how any of this works.

00:08:37.717 --> 00:08:41.869
I just know it's important to Grandpa.

00:08:41.989 --> 00:08:43.089
That's about it.

00:08:43.950 --> 00:08:46.259
Cameras are more
complicated than they look.

00:08:47.349 --> 00:08:50.430
Though I do wish I understood them.

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.460
You wish you understood...?

00:08:54.109 --> 00:08:58.859
You know... I really do love
Grandpa, despite how I act.

00:09:01.239 --> 00:09:02.239
That's wonderful.

00:09:02.359 --> 00:09:03.359
You think so?

00:09:42.299 --> 00:09:45.142
What's wrong with my boy?

00:09:46.280 --> 00:09:47.620
Are you feeling okay?

00:09:49.609 --> 00:09:51.009
Is it the change in seasons?

00:09:51.330 --> 00:09:52.650
Or maybe the barometric pressure?

00:09:54.440 --> 00:09:55.440
Oh.

00:09:55.630 --> 00:09:56.312
Come to think of it,

00:09:56.313 --> 00:09:59.549
I heard Minato's grandfather
was in the hospital recently.

00:09:59.575 --> 00:10:01.618
- Oh dear...
- Wait, what?

00:10:01.643 --> 00:10:03.690
- Hmm?
- How did you know that?

00:10:03.780 --> 00:10:04.880
About Minato's family?

00:10:04.975 --> 00:10:06.158
Oh, the other day...

00:10:06.159 --> 00:10:07.558
I went to lunch with Shio-kun's mom.

00:10:07.559 --> 00:10:08.650
She's the one who told me.

00:10:09.140 --> 00:10:10.140
Oh.

00:10:10.260 --> 00:10:11.890
Apparently, he's already back home.

00:10:12.124 --> 00:10:13.825
- Why...
- The family is taking turns caring for him.

00:10:13.849 --> 00:10:14.849
Why?

00:10:14.950 --> 00:10:16.759
Why am I hearing about
something this important...

00:10:16.760 --> 00:10:18.409
from someone else?

00:10:18.779 --> 00:10:21.120
Being too considerate can be a problem.

00:10:34.071 --> 00:10:37.690
I guess it's because I'm the one
who said we should just be friends.

00:10:48.320 --> 00:10:51.369
It feels wrong for me to reach out first.

00:10:57.590 --> 00:10:58.690
From now on,

00:10:58.765 --> 00:11:01.030
there will be more and
more things I don't know.

00:11:06.559 --> 00:11:07.970
Will he start dating someone...

00:11:08.580 --> 00:11:10.700
without me ever knowing?

00:11:19.020 --> 00:11:20.689
If something happens to him,

00:11:21.330 --> 00:11:24.370
will he not even tell me anymore?

00:11:26.700 --> 00:11:27.800
It's possible...

00:11:36.460 --> 00:11:38.120
that in Minato's future,

00:11:39.869 --> 00:11:41.610
I'm already gone.

00:11:50.409 --> 00:11:51.939
I don't love him anymore.

00:11:53.419 --> 00:11:55.009
Wataru is just a friend.

00:11:55.830 --> 00:11:57.400
Wataru is just a friend...

00:11:58.479 --> 00:12:00.080
Wataru is just a friend...

00:12:01.669 --> 00:12:02.769
I don't love him.

00:12:03.289 --> 00:12:04.780
I don't love him anymore.

00:12:06.239 --> 00:12:07.740
Wataru is just a friend...

00:12:43.169 --> 00:12:44.169
Minato...

00:12:44.250 --> 00:12:45.250
Let's go.

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:56.650
Stop thinking about it.

00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:05.100
(October 17, 2025)

00:13:15.239 --> 00:13:16.239
Just stop.

00:13:26.729 --> 00:13:28.029
Whoa.

00:13:28.919 --> 00:13:30.019
It's beautiful.

00:13:51.869 --> 00:13:52.869
I can't.

00:14:18.400 --> 00:14:20.820
I've already decided we're
going back to being best friends.

00:15:20.528 --> 00:15:21.758
Let's eat.

00:15:35.179 --> 00:15:36.589
At the very last moment,

00:15:37.059 --> 00:15:38.259
I should have just said it.

00:15:41.000 --> 00:15:42.090
I...

00:15:42.359 --> 00:15:43.629
want to be with Wataru...

00:15:46.890 --> 00:15:48.869
I want to spend my life with you.

00:15:51.299 --> 00:15:52.299
Wataru?

00:15:52.400 --> 00:15:53.400
Yes?

00:15:53.609 --> 00:15:55.066
We don't have any more appointments today.

00:15:55.090 --> 00:15:57.428
- You can head out early if you want.
- Okay.

00:15:57.675 --> 00:15:59.840
Oh, can I use the darkroom?

00:16:00.359 --> 00:16:01.359
Go ahead.

00:16:01.380 --> 00:16:02.450
Thanks.

00:16:07.100 --> 00:16:10.200
(October 18, 2025)

00:17:17.780 --> 00:17:19.200
We're best friends.

00:17:20.428 --> 00:17:21.499
We...

00:17:21.948 --> 00:17:23.929
We'll always be best
friends, just like before.

00:17:25.208 --> 00:17:26.488
This is for the best.

00:17:38.280 --> 00:17:40.660
I wish I could just
split my brain in two...

00:17:43.965 --> 00:17:46.370
Wataru, you're still here?

00:17:46.880 --> 00:17:47.934
You too, Boss.

00:17:55.435 --> 00:17:56.709
*Sigh*

00:17:57.859 --> 00:17:59.089
That's a first.

00:17:59.459 --> 00:18:01.093
I've never heard you sigh like that.

00:18:03.560 --> 00:18:04.816
Well...

00:18:05.900 --> 00:18:07.180
You see...

00:18:08.109 --> 00:18:09.959
Remember how I said...

00:18:10.109 --> 00:18:11.300
I was already a grown-up?

00:18:13.239 --> 00:18:14.239
About that...

00:18:14.439 --> 00:18:15.779
I was wrong.

00:18:18.280 --> 00:18:21.069
Apparently, being in the senior
class doesn't make you an adult.

00:18:22.770 --> 00:18:23.870
Oh...

00:18:24.359 --> 00:18:25.530
I see.

00:18:26.040 --> 00:18:28.089
Hmm... Oh!

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:30.609
There you are.

00:18:31.790 --> 00:18:32.990
He looks like...

00:18:33.459 --> 00:18:36.298
he's got a lot on his mind.

00:18:36.323 --> 00:18:38.939
Oh, that's because...

00:18:41.140 --> 00:18:42.740
- Can I tell him?
- Yeah.

00:18:43.739 --> 00:18:44.739
Today,

00:18:44.900 --> 00:18:47.580
he got rejected by his preschool teacher.

00:18:48.520 --> 00:18:49.520
Oh, man...

00:18:50.650 --> 00:18:52.000
Teacher Megumi...

00:18:52.689 --> 00:18:54.270
She's getting married.

00:18:55.260 --> 00:18:58.630
She said I can't marry her
because I'm not an adult.

00:19:00.010 --> 00:19:01.010
I see...

00:19:02.180 --> 00:19:05.755
Well, congratulations to her.

00:19:06.810 --> 00:19:10.318
There's been a lot of good news lately.

00:19:14.459 --> 00:19:15.760
There, there.

00:19:18.329 --> 00:19:19.439
It's okay.

00:19:22.979 --> 00:19:26.472
- I can't say congratulations.
- I know.

00:19:27.040 --> 00:19:28.949
It's all going to disappear.

00:19:30.069 --> 00:19:31.069
Hmm?

00:19:33.790 --> 00:19:34.990
What is?

00:19:36.199 --> 00:19:37.819
The special time...

00:19:38.930 --> 00:19:40.579
I spent with her.

00:19:42.930 --> 00:19:43.930
Kazuma.

00:19:51.430 --> 00:19:52.939
Things might change...

00:19:53.180 --> 00:19:54.840
in the future.

00:19:55.640 --> 00:19:57.870
But the time you cherished in the past...

00:19:58.280 --> 00:19:59.679
that never disappears.

00:20:00.910 --> 00:20:02.010
It will all...

00:20:02.390 --> 00:20:04.100
always be a part of who you are.

00:20:06.650 --> 00:20:07.650
Wataru.

00:20:08.130 --> 00:20:11.729
You sounded like such an
adult just now. It surprised me.

00:20:13.099 --> 00:20:15.220
Hey, I *am* an adult, you know.

00:20:15.729 --> 00:20:16.933
When you care about someone...

00:20:16.934 --> 00:20:18.340
and you'd do anything for them...

00:20:18.900 --> 00:20:20.940
maybe that's when you're
closest to being an adult.

00:20:25.920 --> 00:20:27.020
Someone, huh...

00:20:28.600 --> 00:20:33.600
(October 19, 2025)

00:20:41.569 --> 00:20:42.569
All this time...

00:20:43.680 --> 00:20:45.930
I've only been thinking about myself.

00:20:47.560 --> 00:20:48.560
I...

00:20:50.239 --> 00:20:51.239
Yeah.

00:20:51.699 --> 00:20:53.330
I don't want Wataru to cry.

00:20:53.859 --> 00:20:55.730
To go back to being just friends...

00:20:56.810 --> 00:20:57.930
I'm going to need some time.

00:20:59.560 --> 00:21:00.564
Does it sting?

00:21:00.565 --> 00:21:02.200
Let's have some milk marshmallows.

00:21:02.790 --> 00:21:04.106
Wataru, you've got a
good look on your face.

00:21:04.130 --> 00:21:06.069
If you want them, eat them all.

00:21:06.219 --> 00:21:07.510
Think of it as a celebration.

00:21:07.680 --> 00:21:08.780
Don't stop now.

00:21:08.819 --> 00:21:10.709
To commemorate your heartbreak, Wataru.

00:21:10.780 --> 00:21:12.220
Even after everything Minato said...

00:21:12.410 --> 00:21:14.490
I love the photos Wataru takes.

00:21:14.890 --> 00:21:16.090
Even ten years from now...

00:21:16.900 --> 00:21:18.769
I'll still be by Wataru's side.

00:21:18.869 --> 00:21:19.869
Even after all that...

00:21:50.310 --> 00:21:51.560
Please marry me.

00:22:37.900 --> 00:22:40.100
- (I want to see you)
- (I want to see you)

00:23:02.560 --> 00:23:04.430
(Next Episode)
Ever since you asked to move in...

00:23:04.431 --> 00:23:06.029
I've been so wrapped up in my own head.

00:23:06.030 --> 00:23:08.008
I really cherished the
time I spent with Minato.

00:23:08.033 --> 00:23:09.828
It was only fun because
it was with you, so...

00:23:09.852 --> 00:23:11.585
I love you, Wataru.

00:23:11.609 --> 00:23:12.573
When it comes to you...

00:23:12.574 --> 00:23:14.489
- I want to understand everything.
- I...